show.title: Overcoming Obstacles : The Counter Attack of Twin Babies
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/7K6C2Y
show.description: Once torn apart by betrayal, a young mother and her newborn twins were left to face a cruel fate. Thought to be lost, the children survive  growing up far from the love they deserved. But destiny has other plans. Years later, the twins return. Behind their innocent smiles lie brave hearts filled with love for the mother they never knew  and a quiet determination to make things right. As they search for the truth and fight for justice, they cross paths with a kind stranger who becomes their strongest ally. This is a heartfelt journey of hope, healing, and the unbreakable bond between a mother and her children  told through the eyes of two remarkable little souls who refuse to let go of love.
